T02D3633:249b-3: bgegs mthar byed kyi sgrub thabs /
T02D3633:249b-4: bcom ldan 'das bgegs mthar byed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3633:249b-5: dang por re zhig sgrub pa pos stan bde ba la nye bar 'dug ste /
T02D3633:250a-0: aam yig dmar po las skyes pa'i nyi ma'i @250a * //
T02D3633:250a-1: dkyil 'khor rang gi snying gar bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3633:250a-2: de'i steng du h'um yig nag po bkod nas /
T02D3633:250a-3: h'um yig las skyes pa'i 'od zer gyis bgegs mthar byed dang /
T02D3633:250a-6: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dmigs nas mi tog la
T02D3633:250a-7: sogs pa rnams kyis yang dag par mchod nas phyag
T02D3633:250a-8: 'tshal te / gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba la sogs pa byas nas /
T02D3633:250a-9: stong pa nyid du bsgom par bya ste /
T02D3633:250a-10: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02D3633:250a-12: de'i rjes la aam yig dmar po las skyes pa'i
T02D3633:250a-13: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h'um yig /
T02D3633:250a-14: de yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje h'um yig
T02D3633:250a-15: gis byin gyis brlab par bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3633:250a-16: h'um yig gi 'od zer gyis bskul nas de bzhin
T02D3633:250a-17: gshegs pa thams cad rab tu gzhug pa sngon du
T02D3633:250a-18: 'gro bas / de thams cad yongs su gyur pa las /
T02D3633:250a-19: bgegs mthar byed bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3633:250a-20: zhabs g-yon brkyang gis bzhugs pa'i bdag nyid zhal gcig pa /
T02D3633:250a-22: sku mdog mthing ga / phyag g-yon pas sdigs mdzub dang /
T02D3633:250a-24: phyag g-yas pa rdo rje 'phyar ba /
T02D3633:250a-26: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du brdzes pa'o //
T02D3633:250a-27: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi thugs kar nyi ma'i
T02D3633:250a-28: dkyil 'khor la h'um yig gis byin gyis brlabs pa'i
T02D3633:250a-29: rdo rje'o // de las byung ba'i bgegs mthar byed
T02D3633:250a-30: spro ba dang bsdu ba'i tshul gyis chu skyes 'dab
T02D3633:250a-31: ma sna tshogs kyi steng du nyi ma la gnas
T02D3633:250a-33: dam tshig la sogs pa'i cho ga sngon du 'gro bas so //
T02D3633:250a-34: 'di gnyis dang gsum dang bzhi'i thun mtshams su bsgom par bya'o ;
T02D3633:250a-35: / aom a'a: bi ghn'anta kri ta h'um /
T02D3633:250a-36: bgegs mthar byed kyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02D3633:250a-39: aa m'a ya shtr'i: wa ru n'a ya bi /
T02D3633:250a-48: ba su dh'a r'a ya phat /
T02D3633:250a-49: be na tsi tra ye sv'a /
T02D3633:250a-52: h'um h'um phem phem sv'a h'a /
